Property.name: FamilyName
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the family name of the participating individual. </summary>

Property.name: GivenNames
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the given names of the participating individual. If there are multiple given names, they should be separated by spaces. </summary>

Property.name: LocalIdentifier
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the unique local identifier of the participating individual. The local identifier must be unique within the authoring organisation (HPI-O). For the document author and responsible health professional, this is conditionally mandatory with the HPI-I as at least one must be specified. </summary>

Property.name: Suffix
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the name suffix of the participating individual. </summary>

Property.name: Title
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the name title of the participating individual. </summary>
